  <brief_title>A Prospective, Multicenter, Randomized Controlled Study of Postoperative Thrombosis Prevention in Patients With Cushing's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Multicenter, Randomized Controlled Study of Postoperative Thrombosis Prevention in Patients With Cushing's Disease</official_title>
