  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with Cushing disease was randomized to 2 groups. After surgery, the patients were
      managed with mechanical prevetion or mechanical prevention plus anticoagulant drugs(LMWH
      followed by rivaroxaban), VTE was observed 24h,5day,4weeks and 12weeks after surgery.Bleeding
      events were also recorded.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
